name: The adventures of Aesthetics Police Department

metadata.name: DEAL AT THE BAR
metadata.description:
The Aesthetic Police Departments got a phone call.
Come quiet and low bass belonged to someone who introduced himself as NO-ONE. He said that he had information about where the Technokalosha gang was hiding with the stolen Papaver flower.
Having made an appointment of the BARBARISCA bar the full complement of aesthetic police got were the fully staffed footwalker car and immediately set for available information.

In the far corner of the bar sat an Asian-looking giant who loved to make origami cranes. With his huge hands, he grabbed some origami sheets out of the cop’s hand and disappeared like a hologram from a sci-fi movie.
The map that remained on the table after the Asian offered a route to an abandoned observatory through a wild poppy forest. That's where the aesthetics police went.

The deal was a success!

The collector will get:
The original file is in high resolution and Large (950х700 mm) colorful print on a canvas signed by the author.
